br />\n點為之不放棄，咁你覺得佢講到點先叫俾左利益出來<br />\n<br />\n根本要求任何候選人公開承諾唔做係冇可能<br />\n<br />\n品客開頭hea做已經俾老鼠成屌</blockquote>"},{"pid":"46242911449abae86c5a2a590a2a24a13d995411","tid":169122,"uid":91259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"睇到d薯粉 咩咩就會比林鄭做 就覺得呢d 好on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母 宜家奶有580 個提名呀 仲收埋幾十個冇拎出來呀 薯片點撚贏呀？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左一個假希望 違背自己立場 去支持一個政見都唔同既建制派仲唔係on9 呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尻達講撚中哂 係呢件事上 泛民 一d 薯數都冇呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f3cb8597437b5cb6a9ca8fbc82b30c460a9fbe","tid":169122,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d1db6f0e569add9b0ec6c3bd3727bdfc25bdbce","tid":169122,"uid":2649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"黃絲又衝哂出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d433236d972571864a5cea474c824418e54ba5","tid":169122,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算你地想投鬍鬚 都唔使肉酸到一開跑就gut個頭出黎狗衝<br />\n你拖到越後就越多政治籌碼同鬍鬚deal..<br />\n你班撚樣day 1就揭開底牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n<br />\n政治交易無問題<br />\nLesser evil無問題<br />\n<br />\n不過而家講到唔支持薯片就係鬼，胡官又係鬼長毛又係鬼<br />\n<br />\n咁叫乜撚野民主？<br />\n你話你泛民自己搞個民間選舉，選完啦，係薯片最高票數，咁你投曬比佢我無意見<br />\n<br />\n而家既情況係傾都未傾過就話支持佢，心諗做乜鳩？<br />\n<br />\n都仲未計薯片究竟比咗咩政治利益比呢班泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba97375af87189f9dc9cbb555303eba8a72b2bc","tid":169122,"uid":4484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:35:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>投曬比你好唔好 ?<br />\n<br 